es-patience-harm\/","url_meta":{"origin":14043,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Musa: Moses hurt by people, but was patient","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was distributing charity when a man from the Ansar said, \u201cBy Allah, Muhammad did not intend to please Allah with this!\u201d I came to the Prophet and told him about it, then anger could be seen on\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2802,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/06\/not-make-muhammad-better-musa\/","url_meta":{"origin":14043,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Musa: Do not make Muhammad superior to Moses","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 6, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: Two people, one Jewish and the other Muslim, fell into dispute and began to abuse one another. The Muslim said, \u201cBy the one who has chosen Muhammad above the worlds!\u201d And the Jew said, \u201cBy the one who has chosen Moses above the worlds!\u201d Then, the Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9897,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/22\/ali-ibn-abi-talib-harun-musa\/","url_meta":{"origin":14043,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Prophets: Ali is to Muhammad as Aaron to Moses","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 22, 2012","format":f